description.narrative: Through Mission Oriented Business Integrated Services (MOBIS), Engility has provided USAID with more than 140 professionals in technical areas such as Economic Growth, Democracy and Governance, Education, Agriculture, Infrastructure, Energy, Youth and Gender, Monitoring and Evaluation, Security, Civil-Military Affairs and Transition, Strategic Planning, Information Technology, Web and Database Development, General Development, Alternative Development, Department of State Liaison, Congressional Affairs, Information Technology, Outreach Coordination and Public Information, and Provincial Reconstruction Team (PRT) Training. Engilitys specialists currently provide key support for USAIDs priority efforts in the Middle East as well as for efforts following the declaration of the end of the Iraq war on December 15, 2011.
